title: $:/plugins/linonetwo/mobile-imessage-layout/ControlPanel/SetTagsOnCreate

You Need to Fill this to use the view. Add a tag, for example, "Chat".

<$let currentTiddler="$:/plugins/linonetwo/mobile-imessage-layout/settings/TagsOnCreate">
  <$macrocall $name="tag-picker" tagField="text"/>
</$let>

This view will show tiddlers with these tags. And tiddler created in this layout will add these tags.
